	* Search+Contacts :
		- Added gender icons.												-MC
		- Better things done for married women.								-MC
		- Deceased members and non-subscribers special treatments.			-MC
		- Mobile is now printed too.										-MC
		- People names are clickable.										-MC
		- Unified template.													-JS

	* Skins:
		- Liteskin.															-XdX

